functionDescription: This function checks if the value 'val' of the 'finishnodeget' structure is not nil, and if so, sets the object 'res' to 'val'. It also sets the return value 'ret' to the type tag of 'val'.

outputInterfaces.name: ret
outputInterfaces.meaning: Pointer to the location where the type tag of 'val' will be stored

inoutInterfaces.name: val
inoutInterfaces.meaning: Pointer to the TValue structure containing the value to be checked and processed

inoutInterfaces.name: res
inoutInterfaces.meaning: Pointer to the TValue structure where the result will be stored if 'val' is not nil
